  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK538">
<l>pukaḻntavai pōṟṟic ceyalvēṇṭuñ ceyyā</l>
<l>tikaḻntārk keḻumaiyu mil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let (a man) observe and do these things which have been praised (by the wise); if he neglects and fails to perform them, for him there will be no (happiness) throughout the seven births.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
